name: UCKeyStateEntryTerminal
desc: Maps from a dead-key state to the Unicode character(s) produced when that state is terminated by a given character key for a 'uchr' resource.

items.name: var charData: UCKeyCharSeq
items.desc: A value of type UCKeyCharSeq specifying the Unicode character(s) produced when a given character key is pressed.

items.name: var curState: UInt16
items.desc: An unsigned 16-bit integer specifying the current dead-key state.
